{"id":380,"ayahs":[{"number":36,"arabic":"فَلَمَّا جَآءَ سُلَيْمَٰنَ قَالَ أَتُمِدُّونَنِ بِمَالٍۢ فَمَآ ءَاتَىٰنِۦَ ٱللَّهُ خَيْرٌۭ مِّمَّآ ءَاتَىٰكُم بَلْ أَنتُم بِهَدِيَّتِكُمْ تَفْرَحُونَ","translation":"Now when [the Queen’s messenger] came unto Solomon, he said: “Do you people mean to add to my wealth? But that which God has given me is [so much] better than all that He has given you! Nay, it is [only such as] you that would rejoice in this gift of yours!","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3195.mp3","surahId":27,"words":[{"id":38301,"position":1,"arabic":"فَلَمَّا","translation":"অতঃপর যখন","audioUrl":"wbw/027_036_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38302,"position":2,"arabic":"جَآءَ","translation":"আসলো (দূত)","audioUrl":"wbw/027_036_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38303,"position":3,"arabic":"سُلَيْمَـٰنَ","translation":"সুলায়মানের (নিকট)","audioUrl":"wbw/027_036_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38304,"position":4,"arabic":"قَالَ","translation":"সে বললো","audioUrl":"wbw/027_036_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38305,"position":5,"arabic":"أَتُمِدُّونَنِ","translation":"\"কি তোমরা কি সাহায্য করছো আমাকে","audioUrl":"wbw/027_036_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38306,"position":6,"arabic":"بِمَالٍۢ","translation":"দিয়ে ধনসম্পদ","audioUrl":"wbw/027_036_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38307,"position":7,"arabic":"فَمَآ","translation":"অথচ যা","audioUrl":"wbw/027_036_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38308,"position":8,"arabic":"ءَاتَىٰنِۦَ","translation":"দিয়েছেন আমাকে","audioUrl":"wbw/027_036_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38309,"position":9,"arabic":"ٱللَّهُ","translation":"আল্লাহ","audioUrl":"wbw/027_036_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38310,"position":10,"arabic":"خَيْرٌۭ","translation":"উত্তম","audioUrl":"wbw/027_036_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38311,"position":11,"arabic":"مِّمَّآ","translation":"তার চেয়ে যা","audioUrl":"wbw/027_036_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38312,"position":12,"arabic":"ءَاتَىٰكُم","translation":"দিয়েছেন তোমাদেরকে","audioUrl":"wbw/027_036_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38313,"position":13,"arabic":"بَلْ","translation":"বরং","audioUrl":"wbw/027_036_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38314,"position":14,"arabic":"أَنتُم","translation":"তোমরা","audioUrl":"wbw/027_036_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38315,"position":15,"arabic":"بِهَدِيَّتِكُمْ","translation":"নিয়ে উপঢৌকন তোমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/027_036_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38316,"position":16,"arabic":"تَفْرَحُونَ","translation":"আনন্দ করো","audioUrl":"wbw/027_036_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38317,"position":17,"arabic":"٣٦","translation":"(৩৬)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":37,"arabic":"ٱرْجِعْ إِلَيْهِمْ فَلَنَأْتِيَنَّهُم بِجُنُودٍۢ لَّا قِبَلَ لَهُم بِهَا وَلَنُخْرِجَنَّهُم مِّنْهَآ أَذِلَّةًۭ وَهُمْ صَٰغِرُونَ","translation":"“Go thou back unto them [that have sent thee]! For, [God says:] ‘We shall most certainly come upon them with forces which they will never be able to withstand, and shall most certainly cause them to be driven from that [land of theirs], despicable and humbled!’”","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3196.mp3","surahId":27,"words":[{"id":39146,"position":1,"arabic":"ٱرْجِعْ","translation":"ফিরে যাও","audioUrl":"wbw/027_037_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39147,"position":2,"arabic":"إِلَيْهِمْ","translation":"নিকট তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/027_037_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39148,"position":3,"arabic":"فَلَنَأْتِيَنَّهُم","translation":"অতঃপর অবশ্যই আমরা কাছে আসবোই তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/027_037_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39149,"position":4,"arabic":"بِجُنُودٍۢ","translation":"সহ এক সৈন্যবাহিনী","audioUrl":"wbw/027_037_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39150,"position":5,"arabic":"لَّا","translation":"নেই","audioUrl":"wbw/027_037_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39151,"position":6,"arabic":"قِبَلَ","translation":"রুখবার শক্তি","audioUrl":"wbw/027_037_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39152,"position":7,"arabic":"لَهُم","translation":"কাছে তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/027_037_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39153,"position":8,"arabic":"بِهَا","translation":"বিষয়ে তার","audioUrl":"wbw/027_037_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39154,"position":9,"arabic":"وَلَنُخْرِجَنَّهُم","translation":"এবং অবশ্যই আমরা বের করবোই তাদেরকে","audioUrl":"wbw/027_037_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39155,"position":10,"arabic":"مِّنْهَآ","translation":"হ'তে সেখান","audioUrl":"wbw/027_037_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39156,"position":11,"arabic":"أَذِلَّةًۭ","translation":"অপমানিত করে","audioUrl":"wbw/027_037_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39157,"position":12,"arabic":"وَهُمْ","translation":"যখন তারা","audioUrl":"wbw/027_037_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39158,"position":13,"arabic":"صَـٰغِرُونَ","translation":"অপদস্হ (হবে)\"","audioUrl":"wbw/027_037_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39159,"position":14,"arabic":"٣٧","translation":"(৩৭)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":38,"arabic":"قَالَ يَٰٓأَيُّهَا ٱلْمَلَؤُا۟ أَيُّكُمْ يَأْتِينِى بِعَرْشِهَا قَبْلَ أَن يَأْتُونِى مُسْلِمِينَ","translation":"[When Solomon learned that the Queen of Sheba was coming,] he said [to his council]: “O you nobles! Which of you can bring me her throne ere she and her followers come unto me in willing surrender to God?”","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3197.mp3","surahId":27,"words":[{"id":39960,"position":1,"arabic":"قَالَ","translation":"(সুলায়মান) বললো","audioUrl":"wbw/027_038_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39961,"position":2,"arabic":"يَـٰٓأَيُّهَا","translation":"\"হে","audioUrl":"wbw/027_038_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39962,"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلْمَلَؤُا۟","translation":"সভাসদবৃন্দ","audioUrl":"wbw/027_038_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39963,"position":4,"arabic":"أَيُّكُمْ","translation":"কে তোমাদের মধ্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/027_038_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39964,"position":5,"arabic":"يَأْتِينِى","translation":"আমার কাছে আসবে","audioUrl":"wbw/027_038_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39965,"position":6,"arabic":"بِعَرْشِهَا","translation":"নিয়ে তার সিংহাসন","audioUrl":"wbw/027_038_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39966,"position":7,"arabic":"قَبْلَ","translation":"এর পূর্বেই","audioUrl":"wbw/027_038_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39967,"position":8,"arabic":"أَن","translation":"যে","audioUrl":"wbw/027_038_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39968,"position":9,"arabic":"يَأْتُونِى","translation":"আমার কাছে তারা আসবে","audioUrl":"wbw/027_038_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39969,"position":10,"arabic":"مُسْلِمِينَ","translation":"আত্মসমর্পণকারী হয়ে\"","audioUrl":"wbw/027_038_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39970,"position":11,"arabic":"٣٨","translation":"(৩৮)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":39,"arabic":"قَالَ عِفْرِيتٌۭ مِّنَ ٱلْجِنِّ أَنَا۠ ءَاتِيكَ بِهِۦ قَبْلَ أَن تَقُومَ مِن مَّقَامِكَ ۖ وَإِنِّى عَلَيْهِ لَقَوِىٌّ أَمِينٌۭ","translation":"Said a bold one of the invisible beings [subject to Solomon]: “I shall bring it to thee ere thou rise from thy council-seat - for, behold, I am powerful enough to do it, [and] worthy of trust!”","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3198.mp3","surahId":27,"words":[{"id":40750,"position":1,"arabic":"قَالَ","translation":"বললো","audioUrl":"wbw/027_039_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40751,"position":2,"arabic":"عِفْرِيتٌۭ","translation":"এক শক্তিশালী জিন","audioUrl":"wbw/027_039_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40752,"position":3,"arabic":"مِّنَ","translation":"মধ্য হ'তে","audioUrl":"wbw/027_039_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40753,"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلْجِنِّ","translation":"জিনদের","audioUrl":"wbw/027_039_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40754,"position":5,"arabic":"أَنَا۠","translation":"\"আমি","audioUrl":"wbw/027_039_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40755,"position":6,"arabic":"ءَاتِيكَ","translation":"আপনার কাছে আসবো","audioUrl":"wbw/027_039_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40756,"position":7,"arabic":"بِهِۦ","translation":"নিয়ে তা","audioUrl":"wbw/027_039_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40757,"position":8,"arabic":"قَبْلَ","translation":"এর পূর্বেই","audioUrl":"wbw/027_039_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40758,"position":9,"arabic":"أَن","translation":"যে","audioUrl":"wbw/027_039_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40759,"position":10,"arabic":"تَقُومَ","translation":"আপনি উঠে দাঁড়াবেন","audioUrl":"wbw/027_039_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40760,"position":11,"arabic":"مِن","translation":"হ'তে","audioUrl":"wbw/027_039_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40761,"position":12,"arabic":"مَّقَامِكَ ۖ","translation":"আপনার স্থান","audioUrl":"wbw/027_039_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40763,"position":13,"arabic":"وَإِنِّى","translation":"এবং নিশ্চয়ই আমি","audioUrl":"wbw/027_039_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40764,"position":14,"arabic":"عَلَيْهِ","translation":"উপর এর","audioUrl":"wbw/027_039_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40765,"position":15,"arabic":"لَقَوِىٌّ","translation":"অবশ্যই শক্তিশালী","audioUrl":"wbw/027_039_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40766,"position":16,"arabic":"أَمِينٌۭ","translation":"বিশ্বস্ত\"","audioUrl":"wbw/027_039_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40767,"position":17,"arabic":"٣٩","translation":"(৩৯)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":40,"arabic":"قَالَ ٱلَّذِى عِندَهُۥ عِلْمٌۭ مِّنَ ٱلْكِتَٰبِ أَنَا۠ ءَاتِيكَ بِهِۦ قَبْلَ أَن يَرْتَدَّ إِلَيْكَ طَرْفُكَ ۚ فَلَمَّا رَءَاهُ مُسْتَقِرًّا عِندَهُۥ قَالَ هَٰذَا مِن فَضْلِ رَبِّى لِيَبْلُوَنِىٓ ءَأَشْكُرُ أَمْ أَكْفُرُ ۖ وَمَن شَكَرَ فَإِنَّمَا يَشْكُرُ لِنَفْسِهِۦ ۖ وَمَن كَفَرَ فَإِنَّ رَبِّى غَنِىٌّۭ كَرِيمٌۭ","translation":"Answered he who was illumined by revela­tion: “[Nay,] as for me - I shall bring it to thee ere the twinkling of thy eye ceases!” And when he saw it truly before him, he exclaimed: “This is [an outcome] of my Sustainer’s bounty, to test me as to whether I am grateful or ungrateful! However, he who is grateful [to God] is but grateful for his own good; and he who is ungrate­ful [should know that], verily, my Sustainer is self-sufficient, most generous in giving!”","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3199.mp3","surahId":27,"words":[{"id":41609,"position":1,"arabic":"قَالَ","translation":"(এরপর)বললো একজন","audioUrl":"wbw/027_040_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41610,"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِى","translation":"সে (এমন যে)","audioUrl":"wbw/027_040_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41611,"position":3,"arabic":"عِندَهُۥ","translation":"নিকট তার (ছিলো)","audioUrl":"wbw/027_040_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41612,"position":4,"arabic":"عِلْمٌۭ","translation":"জ্ঞান","audioUrl":"wbw/027_040_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41613,"position":5,"arabic":"مِّنَ","translation":"থেকে","audioUrl":"wbw/027_040_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41614,"position":6,"arabic":"ٱلْكِتَـٰبِ","translation":"কিতাবের","audioUrl":"wbw/027_040_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41615,"position":7,"arabic":"أَنَا۠","translation":"\"আমি","audioUrl":"wbw/027_040_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41616,"position":8,"arabic":"ءَاتِيكَ","translation":"আপনার কাছে আসবো","audioUrl":"wbw/027_040_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41617,"position":9,"arabic":"بِهِۦ","translation":"নিয়ে তা","audioUrl":"wbw/027_040_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41618,"position":10,"arabic":"قَبْلَ","translation":"(এর) পূর্বেই","audioUrl":"wbw/027_040_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41619,"position":11,"arabic":"أَن","translation":"যে","audioUrl":"wbw/027_040_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41620,"position":12,"arabic":"يَرْتَدَّ","translation":"ফিরবে","audioUrl":"wbw/027_040_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":