 যে","audioUrl":"wbw/027_040_030.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41639,"position":29,"arabic":"شَكَرَ","translation":"কৃতজ্ঞ হয়","audioUrl":"wbw/027_040_031.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41640,"position":30,"arabic":"فَإِنَّمَا","translation":"তবে শুধুমাত্র","audioUrl":"wbw/027_040_032.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41641,"position":31,"arabic":"يَشْكُرُ","translation":"সে কৃতজ্ঞ হয়","audioUrl":"wbw/027_040_033.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41642,"position":32,"arabic":"لِنَفْسِهِۦ ۖ","translation":"জন্যে তার নিজের","audioUrl":"wbw/027_040_034.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41644,"position":33,"arabic":"وَمَن","translation":"আর যে","audioUrl":"wbw/027_040_036.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41645,"position":34,"arabic":"كَفَرَ","translation":"অকৃতজ্ঞ হয়","audioUrl":"wbw/027_040_037.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41646,"position":35,"arabic":"فَإِنَّ","translation":"তবে নিশ্চয়ই","audioUrl":"wbw/027_040_038.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41647,"position":36,"arabic":"رَبِّى","translation":"আমার রব","audioUrl":"wbw/027_040_039.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41648,"position":37,"arabic":"غَنِىٌّۭ","translation":"অভাবমুক্ত","audioUrl":"wbw/027_040_040.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41649,"position":38,"arabic":"كَرِيمٌۭ","translation":"সম্মানিত\"","audioUrl":"wbw/027_040_041.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41650,"position":39,"arabic":"٤٠","translation":"(৪০)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":41,"arabic":"قَالَ نَكِّرُوا۟ لَهَا عَرْشَهَا نَنظُرْ أَتَهْتَدِىٓ أَمْ تَكُونُ مِنَ ٱلَّذِينَ لَا يَهْتَدُونَ","translation":"[And] he continued: Alter her throne so that she may not know it as hers: let us see whether she allows herself to be guided [to the truth] or remains one of those who will not be guided.”","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3200.mp3","surahId":27,"words":[{"id":42458,"position":1,"arabic":"قَالَ","translation":"(সুলায়মান) বললো","audioUrl":"wbw/027_041_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42459,"position":2,"arabic":"نَكِّرُوا۟","translation":"\"তোমরা অজ্ঞাতসারে রাখো","audioUrl":"wbw/027_041_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42460,"position":3,"arabic":"لَهَا","translation":"সামনে তার","audioUrl":"wbw/027_041_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42461,"position":4,"arabic":"عَرْشَهَا","translation":"সিংহাসন তার","audioUrl":"wbw/027_041_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42462,"position":5,"arabic":"نَنظُرْ","translation":"দেখবো আমরা","audioUrl":"wbw/027_041_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42463,"position":6,"arabic":"أَتَهْتَدِىٓ","translation":"সে (সঠিক) ব্যাপার বুঝতে পারছে কি","audioUrl":"wbw/027_041_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42464,"position":7,"arabic":"أَمْ","translation":"অথবা","audioUrl":"wbw/027_041_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42465,"position":8,"arabic":"تَكُونُ","translation":"সে হয়","audioUrl":"wbw/027_041_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42466,"position":9,"arabic":"مِنَ","translation":"অন্তর্ভুক্ত","audioUrl":"wbw/027_041_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42467,"position":10,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ","translation":"(তাদের) যারা","audioUrl":"wbw/027_041_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42468,"position":11,"arabic":"لَا","translation":"না\"","audioUrl":"wbw/027_041_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42469,"position":12,"arabic":"يَهْتَدُونَ","translation":"পথ পায়\"","audioUrl":"wbw/027_041_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42470,"position":13,"arabic":"٤١","translation":"(৪১)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":42,"arabic":"فَلَمَّا جَآءَتْ قِيلَ أَهَٰكَذَا عَرْشُكِ ۖ قَالَتْ كَأَنَّهُۥ هُوَ ۚ وَأُوتِينَا ٱلْعِلْمَ مِن قَبْلِهَا وَكُنَّا مُسْلِمِينَ","translation":"And so, as soon as she arrived, she was asked: “Is thy throne like this?” She answered: “It is as though it were the same!” [And Solomon said to his nobles: “She has arrived at the truth without any help from us,] although it is we who have been given [divine] knowledge before her, and have [long ago] surrendered ourselves unto God!","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3201.mp3","surahId":27,"words":[{"id":43133,"position":1,"arabic":"فَلَمَّا","translation":"অতঃপর যখন","audioUrl":"wbw/027_042_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":43134,"position":2,"arabic":"جَآءَتْ","translation":"(রানী) আসলো","audioUrl":"wbw/027_042_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":43135,"position":3,"arabic":"قِيلَ","translation":"বলা হলো","audioUrl":"wbw/027_042_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":43136,"position":4,"arabic":"أَهَـٰكَذَا","translation":"\"এরূপই কি","audioUrl":"wbw/027_042_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":43137,"position":5,"arabic":"عَرْشُكِ ۖ","translation":"তোমার সিংহাসন\"","audioUrl":"wbw/027_042_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":43139,"position":6,"arabic":"قَالَتْ","translation":"সে বললো","audioUrl":"wbw/027_042_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":43140,"position":7,"arabic":"كَأَنَّهُۥ","translation":"\"এ যেন","audioUrl":"wbw/027_042_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":43141,"position":8,"arabic":"هُوَ ۚ","translation":"সেটাই\"","audioUrl":"wbw/027_042_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":43143,"position":9,"arabic":"وَأُوتِينَا","translation":"\"এবং আমাদের দেয়া হয়েছে","audioUrl":"wbw/027_042_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":43144,"position":10,"arabic":"ٱلْعِلْمَ","translation":"জ্ঞান","audioUrl":"wbw/027_042_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":43145,"position":11,"arabic":"مِن","translation":"থেকেই","audioUrl":"wbw/027_042_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":43146,"position":12,"arabic":"قَبْلِهَا","translation":"এর পূর্ব","audioUrl":"wbw/027_042_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":43147,"position":13,"arabic":"وَكُنَّا","translation":"এবং আমরা ছিলাম","audioUrl":"wbw/027_042_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":43148,"position":14,"arabic":"مُسْلِمِينَ","translation":"আত্মসমর্পণকারী\"","audioUrl":"wbw/027_042_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":43149,"position":15,"arabic":"٤٢","translation":"(৪২)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":43,"arabic":"وَصَدَّهَا مَا كَانَت تَّعْبُدُ مِن دُونِ ٱللَّهِ ۖ إِنَّهَا كَانَتْ مِن قَوْمٍۢ كَٰفِرِينَ","translation":"[And she has recognized the truth] although that which she has been wont to worship instead of God had kept her away [from the right path]: for, behold, she is descended of people who deny the truth!”","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3202.mp3","surahId":27,"words":[{"id":43876,"position":1,"arabic":"وَصَدَّهَا","translation":"আর তাকে বিরত রেখেছিলো (ঈমান আনা হ'তে)","audioUrl":"wbw/027_043_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":43877,"position":2,"arabic":"مَا","translation":"(তাই) যা কিছু","audioUrl":"wbw/027_043_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":43878,"position":3,"arabic":"كَانَت","translation":"সে ছিলো","audioUrl":"wbw/027_043_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":43879,"position":4,"arabic":"تَّعْبُدُ","translation":"সে পূজা করে","audioUrl":"wbw/027_043_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":43880,"position":5,"arabic":"مِن","translation":"থেকে","audioUrl":"wbw/027_043_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":43881,"position":6,"arabic":"دُونِ","translation":"ছাড়া","audioUrl":"wbw/027_043_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":43882,"position":7,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ ۖ","translation":"আল্লাহ","audioUrl":"wbw/027_043_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":43884,"position":8,"arabic":"إِنَّهَا","translation":"নিশ্চয়ই সে","audioUrl":"wbw/027_043_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":43885,"position":9,"arabic":"كَانَتْ","translation":"ছিলো","audioUrl":"wbw/027_043_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":43886,"position":10,"arabic":"مِن","translation":"অন্তর্ভুক্ত","audioUrl":"wbw/027_043_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":43887,"position":11,"arabic":"قَوْمٍۢ","translation":"জাতির","audioUrl":"wbw/027_043_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":43888,"position":12,"arabic":"كَـٰفِرِينَ","translation":"কাফের","audioUrl":"wbw/027_043_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":43889,"position":13,"arabic":"٤٣","translation":"(৪৩)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":44,"arabic":"قِيلَ لَهَا ٱدْخُلِى ٱلصَّرْحَ ۖ فَلَمَّا رَأَتْهُ حَسِبَتْهُ لُجَّةًۭ وَكَشَفَتْ عَن سَاقَيْهَا ۚ قَالَ إِنَّهُۥ صَرْحٌۭ مُّمَرَّدٌۭ مِّن قَوَارِيرَ ۗ قَالَتْ رَبِّ إِنِّى ظَلَمْتُ نَفْسِى وَأَسْلَمْتُ مَعَ سُلَيْمَٰنَ لِلَّهِ رَبِّ ٱلْعَٰلَمِينَ","translation":"[After a while] she was told: “Enter this court!” - but when she saw it, she thought that it was a fathomless expanse of water, and she bared her legs. Said he: “Behold, it is [but] a court smoothly paved with glass!” Cried she: “O my Sustainer! I have been sinning against myself thy worshipping aught but Thee]: but [now] I have surrendered myself, with Solomon, unto the Sustainer of all the worlds!”","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3203.mp3","surahId":27,"words":[{"id":44626,"position":1,"arabic":"قِيلَ","translation":"বলা হলো","audioUrl":"wbw/027_044_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":44627,"position":2,"arabic":"لَهَا","translation":"উদ্দেশ্যে তার","audioUrl":"wbw/027_044_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":44628,"position":3,"arabic":"ٱدْخُلِى","translation":"\"প্রবেশ করো","audioUrl":"wbw/027_044_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":44629,"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلصَّرْحَ ۖ","translation":"(এই) প্রাসাদে\"","audioUrl":"wbw/027_044_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":44631,"position":5,"arabic":"فَلَمَّا","translation":"অতঃপর যখন","audioUrl":"wbw/027_044_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":44632,"position":6,"arabic":"رَأَتْهُ","translation":"তা সে দেখলো","audioUrl":"wbw/027_044_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":44633,"position":7,"arabic":"حَسِبَتْهُ","translation":"তা মনে করলো","audioUrl":"wbw/027_044_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":44634,"position":8,"arabic":"لُجَّةًۭ","translation":"পানির হাউজ (জলাশয়)","audioUrl":"wbw/027_044_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":44635,"position":9,"arabic":"وَكَشَفَتْ","translation":"ও উঠালো (কাপড়)","audioUrl":"wbw/027_044_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":44636,"position":10,"arabic":"عَن","translation":"হতে","audioUrl":"wbw/027_044_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":44637,"position":11,"arabic":"سَاقَيْهَا ۚ","translation":"দুই গোড়ালী তার","audioUrl":"wbw/027_044_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":44639,"position":12,"arabic":"قَالَ","translation":"(সুলায়মান) বললো","audioUrl":"wbw/027_044_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":44640,"position":13,"arabic":"إِنَّهُۥ","translation":"\"নিশ্চয় তা","audioUrl":"wbw/027_044_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":44641,"position":14,"arabic":"صَرْحٌۭ","translation":"(প্রাসাদের) মেঝে","audioUrl":"wbw/027_044_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":44642,"position":15,"arabic":"مُّمَرَّدٌۭ","translation":"নির্মিত","audioUrl":"wbw/027_044_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":44643,"position":16,"arabic":"مِّن","translation":"দিয়ে","audioUrl":"wbw/027_044_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":44644,"position":17,"arabic":"قَوَارِيرَ ۗ","translation":"স্বচ্ছ কাঁচ\"","audioUrl":"wbw/027_044_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":44646,"position":18,"arabic":"قَالَتْ","translation":"(রানী) বললো","audioUrl":"wbw/027_044_021.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":44647,"position":19,"arabic":"رَبِّ","translation":"\"হে আমার রব (আজ পর্যন্ত)","audioUrl":"wbw/027_044_022.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":44648,"position":20,"arabic":"إِنِّى","translation":"নিশ্চয়ই আমি","audioUrl":"wbw/027_044_023.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":44649,"position":21,"arabic":"ظَلَمْتُ","translation":"অন্যায় করেছি","audioUrl":"wbw/027_044_024.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":44650,"position":22,"arabic":"نَفْسِى","translation":"আমার নিজের (উপর)","audioUrl":"wbw/027_044_025.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":44651,"position":23,"arabic":"وَأَسْلَمْتُ","translation":"(আর এখন) আমি আত্মসমর্পণ করছি","audioUrl":"wbw/027_044_026.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":44652,"position":24,"arabic":"مَعَ","translation":"সাথে","audioUrl":"wbw/027_044_027